# If you use DOS-style suffixes, you may want to uncomment the following:
#.bat 01;32 # executables (bright green)
#.btm 01;32
#.cmd 01;32
#.com 01;32
#.exe 01;32
# Or if you want to colorize scripts even if they do not have the executable bit actually set.
#.csh 01;32
#.sh  01;32
#.zsh 01;32
